headline: Union Pacific Corporation CEO Jim Vena and CFO Jennifer Hamann to Address the Baird 2025 Global Industrial Conference
summary: OMAHA, Neb., November 04, 2025--Jim Vena, chief executive officer and Jennifer Hamann, executive vice president and chief financial officer, of Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE: UNP) will address the Baird 2025 Global Industrial Conference on Tuesday, Nov. 11, 2025, at 2:45 p.m. ET.
